/-- **The tower rungs obey the Lucasâ€“Lehmer recurrence.** `D_{2^(k+1)} =
(D_{2^k})آ² âˆ’ 2`: the Salem 2-adic tower is generated by `s â†¦ sآ² âˆ’ 2`, exactly the
